Interest: netflix, kim da mi, netflix sci-fi blockbuster movie, the great flood
Narrative: "The Great Flood" depicts the struggle of people trying to save humanity in an apartment that is submerged in water following a great flood. Kim Dami will take the role of Anna, an artificial intelligence development researcher who struggles to survive within a great flood. Park Hae Soo will act as Hee Jo who works in the Human Resources Security Team, trying to rescue Anna from the great flood that threatens the entire planet.
Title: Kim Da Mi & Park Hae Soo to lead upcoming Netflix sci-fi blockbuster movie 'The Great Flood'
